Skater%203%2B4%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20remake%20of%20the%202001-2002%20games%20where%20your%20character%20wheels%20around%20various%20skate%20spots%2C%20completing%20tricks%20and%20missions%2C%20drops%20Friday).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20he's%20pushing%2060%20is%20such%20a%20strange%20concept%20that%20it's%20an%20inside%20joke%20between%20him%20and%20fans%20who%20pretend%20not%20to%20recognize%20him.%20How%20could%20Tony%20Hawk%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kid%20at%20the%20skatepark%20who%20was%20imaginative%2C%20dogged%2C%20and%20dumb%20enough%20to%20pull%20off%20the%20types%20of%20tricks%20that%20helped%20skating%20go%20mainstream%20in%20the%20'80s%20and%20'90s%20%E2%80%94%20get%20old%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20documentary%20%26quot%3BTony%20Hawk%3A%20Until%20the%20Wheels%20Fall%20Off%26quot%3B%20explores%20this%20tension.%20His%20friends%20say%20they%20hope%20he'll%20soon%20slow%20down%20over%20footage%20of%20him%20repeatedly%20smashing%20to%20the%20ground%20as%20he%20tries%20to%20recreate%20what's%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftony-hawk-talks-skateboarding-olympics-culture-parenting-influence-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20900%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%201999%2C%20Hawk%20landed%20the%20trick%20%E2%80%94%20which%20involves%20spinning%20900%20degrees%20midair%20%E2%80%94%20after%20trying%20for%20a%20decade.%20Before%20that%2C%20skaters%20had%20only%20dreamed%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20recalls%20seriously%20breaking%20his%20leg%20in%202022%20during%20our%20call%2C%20it's%20clear%20there%20are%20two%20Tonys%3A%20pre-and%20post-break%20Tony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20no%20stranger%20to%20injuries%2C%20but%20snapping%20your%20femur%20in%20half%20at%2053%20is%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20sounds%2C%20and%20it%20took%20him%2012%20months%20to%20recover.%20Becoming%20a%20grandad%20was%20another%20profound%20change.%20(His%20son%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftony-hawk-advice-for-so