and%20adapt%20them%20in%20response%20to%20changing%20battlefield%20conditions%20creates%20a%20model%20that%20other%20militaries%20are%20striving%20now%20to%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryan%20Clark%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20small%20FPV%20drones%20used%20by%20both%20sides%20may%20not%20have%20utility%20in%20a%20war%20against%20China%2C%20the%20approach%20of%20building%20systems%20on%20demand%20using%20modular%20components%20is%20beginning%20to%20emerge%20in%20the%20US%20industrial%20base%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20has%20been%20made%20possible%20by%20Ukraine%20upending%20traditional%20military%20procurement%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNecessity%20and%20urgency%20breed%20true%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Emily%20Harding%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20defense%20and%20security%20department%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20has%20found%20a%20way%20to%20upend%20normal%20cycles%20of%20development%20and%20procurement%20to%20get%20troops%20updated%20equipment%20within%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20aspect%20has%20been%20to%20directly%20connect%20defense%20startups%20with%20soldiers%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinking%20companies%20directly%20with%20units%20in%20the%20field%20turns%20the%20innovation%20cycle%20into%20a%20flywheel%20%E2%80%94%20rapid%20feedback%2C%20adaptation%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20deployment%20to%20the%20front%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20Harding%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Klain%2C%20a%20nonresident%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Eurasia%20Center%2C%20argues%20that%20Ukraine%20isn't%20just%20catching%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20pointing%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20American%20defense%20producers%20take%20years%20to%20iterate%20and%20update%20systems%20based%20on%20testing%20before%20redeploying%2C%20Ukrainians%20are%20making%20significant%20updates%20within%20weeks%20to%20overcome%20Russian%20countermeasures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ukraine's%20shift%20toward%20indigenous%20production%20is%20accelerating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20that%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-shifting-strategy-boost-ukraine-weapons-defense-production-russia-war-2025-4%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E40%25%20of%20Ukraine's%20weapons%20now%20come%20from%20domestic%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20impressive%20figure%20for%20a%20country%20under%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlain%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20also%20becoming%20more%20than%20just%20the%20frontline%20of%20Europe's%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFar%20from%20being%20a%20recipient%20of%20assistance%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20a%20value-add%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20more%20experienced%20army%20in%20resisting%20Russian%20aggression%20today%2C%20and%20its%20defense%20industry%20is%20increasingly%20tailored%20to%20the%20scale%20and%20specialties%20required%20for%20defending%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20defense%20startups%20like%20TenCore%20%E2%80%94%20founded%20in%20early%202024%20with%20five%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20highlight%20this%20shift.%20With%20175%20employees%20and%20projecting%20%2480%20million%20in%20revenue%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20delivered%20more%20than%202%2C000%20battlefield%20systems%20and%20turned%20down%20acquisition%20offers%20to%20remain%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20militaries%20are%20taking%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20innovative%20use%20of%20drones%20and%20other%20AI-enabled%20autonomous%20systems%20has%20%26quot%3Brevolutionized%20the%20role%20these%20technologies%20play%20in%20modern%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20from%20logistics%20to%20long-range%20strikes%2C%26quot%3B%20Lauren%20Speranza%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModern%20war%20between%20peer%20competitors%20is%20clearly%20a%20war%20of%20defense%20industrial%20bases%20as%20much%20as%20of%20men%20and%20maneuver%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Harding.%20%26quot%3BA%20country%20that%20cannot%20adapt%20to%20developments%20on%20the%20battlefield%20and%20sustain%20the%20warfighters%20is%20sure%20to%20lose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20military%20experts%20caution%20against%20wholesale%20replication%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWestern%20militaries%20can't%20over-index%20on%20what%20Ukraine%20is%20doing%20in%20terms%20of%20specific%20systems%20because%20the%20conditions%20are%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20Hudson%20Institute's%20Clark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20leveraging%20militarily%20relevant%20commercial%20technology%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20essential%20for%20gaining%20an%20advantage%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELessons%20may%20also%20extend%20to%20how%20future%20wars%20are%20conceptualized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20has%20effectively%20replaced%20artillery%20with%20drones%20for%20entrenched%20warfare%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20O'Hanlon%2C%20director%20of%20research%20in%20foreign%20policy%20at%20the%20Brookings%20Institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20change%20everything%20about%20modern%20combat%2C%20but%20it%20changes%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20points%20the%20way%20to%20future%20close-in%20fights%20where%20drone%20swarms%20may%20dominate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Ukraine's%20ability%20to%20scale%20remains%20limited%20by%20one%20major%20factor%3A%20money.%20With%20a%20%2412%20billion%20defense%20budget%2C%20officials%20estimate%20that%20the%20country's%20production%20capacity%20is%20a%20third%20of%20its%20true%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyiv%20is%20now%20pushing%20to%20attract%20more%20Western%20investment%20and%20is%20eyeing%20initiatives%20like%20the%20EU's%20proposed%20SAFE%20project%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%24150%20billion%20fund%20designed%20to%20strengthen%20European%20defense%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20integral%20in%20any%20future%20European%20security%20architecture%2C%26quot%3B%20Klain%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20genuine%20lessons%20to%20offer%20as%20we%20all%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20revitalize%20defense%20industries%20that%20just%20aren't%20up%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20modern%20warfare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-defense-industry-changing-how-west-thinks-about-war-russia-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752070433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a609a3bfebcc4d029e293d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-defense-industry-changing-how-west-thinks-about-war-russia-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20booming%20defense%20industry%20is%20revolutionizing%20modern%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reshaping%20how%20Western%20militaries%20think%2C%20build%2C%20and%20potentially%20fight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A57%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-defense-industry-changing-how-west-thinks-about-war-russia-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%20Gets%20Green%20Light%20From%20Indian%20Space%20Regulator%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22In%20what%20could%20change%20the%20future%20of%20affordable%20satellite-based%20internet%20service%20in%20India%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%20on%20Wednesday