rly%20access%20to%20new%20mods.%20Asking%20for%20donations%20instead%20of%20mandatory%20payments%20lets%20modders%20profit%20without%20violating%20most%20games'%20end-user%20license%20agreements%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20freedom%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20hobby%20they%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIlja%20Jusupov%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgraphtreon.com%2Ftop-patreon-creators%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird%20biggest%20creator%20on%20Patreon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20started%20out%20by%20modding%20the%20shooting%20game%20%26quot%3BS.T.A.L.K.E.R.%3A%20Shadow%20of%20Chernobyl%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20texture%20packs%20and%20menus%20to%20configure%20other%20mods.%20He%20already%20had%20some%20programming%20experience%2C%20but%20modding%20is%20what%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20after%20he%20started%20making%20mods%20for%20the%20racing%20game%20%26quot%3BAssetto%20Corsa%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20put%20his%20projects%20on%20Patreon%2C%20where%20he's%20since%20found%20success.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fx4fab%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJusupov's%20Patreon%3C%2Fa%3E%20brings%20in%20nearly%20%2450%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20he%20attributes%20to%20the%20passionate%20fan%20base%20for%20%26quot%3BAssetto%20Corsa%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20consistency%20of%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJusupov%20said%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20running%20a%20successful%20Patreon%20as%20a%20modder%20are%20consistently%20preparing%20new%20updates%20to%20satisfy%20subscribers%20and%20responding%20to%20the%20feedback%20those%20subscribers%20give%20without%20sacrificing%20independence.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20create%20an%20impression%20that%20we're%20not%20addressing%20our%20patrons'%20demands%2C%20but%20also%20still%20want%20to%20pursue%20new%20horizons%20and%20bring%20something%20new%20on%20a%20semi-regular%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20modders%20looking%20to%20find%20independent%20success%2C%20he%20recommended%20targeting%20%26quot%3Bniche%26quot%3B%20games%20and%20taking%20on%20projects%20that%20you're%20passionate%20about.%20%26quot%3BA%20modification%20for%20'GTA%205'%20would%20guarantee%20a%20large%20user%20base%2C%20but%20I%20imagine%20something%20smaller%20could%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20unsolved%20demands%20users%20would%20love%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViktor%20%26quot%3BNSGolova%26quot%3B%20Radulov%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20modder%20for%20the%20virtual%20reality%20rhythm%20game%20%26quot%3BBeat%20Saber%2C%26quot%3B%20similarly%20said%20creators%20should%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20on%20helping%20players%20first%20and%20monetize%20later.%20If%20people%20are%20happy%20with%20your%20mods%2C%20they'll%20be%20happy%20to%20donate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadulov's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FBeatLeader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatreon%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20include%20mods%20to%20add%20cosmetics%20and%20a%20leaderboard%20to%20the%20game%2C%20earn%20him%20over%20%244%2C500%20a%20month.%20He%20began%20his%20programming%20career%20developing%20add-ons%20for%20Mac%20and%20iOS%2C%20and%20his%20interest%20in%20%26quot%3BBeat%20Saber%26quot%3B%20led%20him%20to%20take%20on%20modding%20as%20a%20hobby.%20While%20modding%20is%20currently%20a%20side%20hustle%20for%20him%2C%20he%20hopes%20to%20eventually%20turn%20modding%20into%20his%20sole%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20monetization%20platforms%20include%20Ko-fi%20and%20Nexus%20Mods.%20The%20latter%20lets%20modders%20earn%20%26quot%3BDonation%20Points%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20redeemed%20for%20gifts%20or%20cash.%20Nexus%20Mods%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20has%20paid%20out%20over%20%2412%20million%20to%20its%20top%20creators%20since%202018.%20Some%20modders%2C%20like%20Dream%20and%20DougDoug%2C%20create%20content%20as%20well%2C%20using%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%