0decided%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20custom%20content%20creation.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20had%20fun%20recoloring%20the%20set%2C%20I%20learned%20more%20about%203D%20modeling%20and%20texturing%2C%20and%20I%20began%20creating%20original%20items.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20I%20opened%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-patreon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatreon%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20to%20help%20me%20pay%20for%20the%20modding%20software%2C%20which%20costs%20about%20%E2%82%AC80%20a%20month.%20My%20subscriptions%20grew%2C%20and%20after%20six%20months%2C%20I%20was%20earning%20enough%20money%20to%20stop%20freelancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20was%20less%20money%20at%20first%2C%20I%20was%20completely%20free.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20clients%2C%20deadlines%2C%20or%20anyone%20to%20tell%20me%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20kept%20a%20few%20freelance%20jobs%20during%20the%20transition%2C%20but%20after%20a%20year%20or%20so%2C%20I%20was%20earning%20more%20than%20I%20did%20in%20my%20advertising%20job%2C%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20never%20going%20back%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20now%20make%20more%20than%20I%20did%20in%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ecbd5c9-f1f3-4fef-a73f-4a835ee5fba5%5C%22%3EMy%20work%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d348c3d5881a51c1cdf18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeroubaix%20said%20modular%20items%2C%20such%20as%20kitchen%20counters%2C%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20items%20to%20create%20in%20The%20Sims%204.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20four%20years%20now.%20Every%20month%20on%20my%20Patreon%2C%20I%20post%20a%20set%2C%20which%20includes%2020%20to%2030%20items%20inspired%20by%20a%20theme%20or%20room.%20All%20of%20my%20subscribers%20get%20early%20access%20to%20my%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20by%20making%20a%20mood%20board%20and%20looking%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-add-notes-on-pinterest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPinterest%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Google%20for%20anything%20that%20inspires%20me.%20Once%20I've%20gathered%20references%2C%20I'll%20pick%20a%20number%20of%20items%20to%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20spread%20my%20work%20throughout%20the%20month.%20I%20can%20create%20one%20item%20in%20five%20to%20eight%20hours%2C%20so%20I%20usually%20make%20one%20per%20day.%20Then%2C%20I%20test%20every%20item%20in%20the%20game%20and%20take%20screenshots%20to%20show%20my%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a6a11bb-5af3-4088-aa20-fda4ad8907a6%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20make%20money%20as%20a%20modder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222050%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d33723d5881a51c1cdead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHer%20Creator%20Kit%2C%20an%20official%20content%20pack%20she%20developed%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Sims%2C%20was%20released%20this%20April.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20games%20endorse%20monetized%20mods.%20The%20Sims%204%20modders%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20officially%20sell%20their%20creations%2C%20but%20The%20Sims%20allows%20modders%20to%20release%20content%20for%20free%20with%20monetized%20early%20access.%20This%20means%20people%20who%20subscribe%20to%20my%20Patreon%20get%20my%20items%20three%20weeks%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20then%20my%20custom%20content%20becomes%20free%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%2C%20I%20o