0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-realreal-is-using-ai-to-find-fakes-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonline%20marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20users%20can%20buy%20and%20sell%20tickets%20for%20concerts%2C%20sports%20games%2C%20and%20other%20live%20events.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287952802-2bb7-4912-8006-7566951200f6%5C%22%3ESituation%20analysis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20fraud-prevention%20systems%20have%20relied%20on%20binary%20yes-or-no%20decisions%20to%20conclude%20whether%20a%20transaction%20is%20real.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20approve%20authentic%20orders%20and%20decline%20fraudulent%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Jeff%20Otto%2C%20Riskified's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20system%20has%20limitations%20and%20is%20often%20too%20rigid%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20evolving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-small-business-owners-swamped-by-scammers-generative-ai-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efraud%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20these%20old%20yes-no%20answers%20get%20it%20right%2C%20and%20it's%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20Otto%20said.%20But%20sometimes%20the%20system%20gets%20it%20wrong%2C%20and%20legitimate%20orders%20are%20falsely%20declined%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtto%20said%20that%20when%20transactions%20are%20falsely%20declined%2C%20it%20can%20be%20frustrating%20for%20customers.%20Each%20time%20it%20happens%2C%20companies%20lose%20the%20sale%2C%20which%20can%20cost%20them%20millions%20of%20dollars%20a%20year.%20False%20declines%20can%20also%20tarnish%20their%20service%20reputation%20when%20customers%20don't%20return%2C%20or%20they%20review%20their%20poor%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20traditional%20fraud-detection%20model%2C%20Riskified%20launched%20Adaptive%20Checkout%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E-powered%20tool%20that%20analyzes%20orders%20in%20real%20time.%20While%20the%20tool%20formally%20launched%20in%20March%202025%2C%20some%20of%20Riskified's%20clients%20tested%20the%20product%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETickPick%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20began%20using%20the%20tool%20in%20the%20testing%20phase%20in%20November%202024%20to%20reduce%20its%20fraud%20risk%20and%20improve%20false%20decline%20rates.%20The%20company%20often%20deals%20with%20%26quot%3Bvery%20large-priced%20tickets%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20%2420%2C000%20Super%20Bowl%20passes%2C%20Otto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20got%20to%20get%20that%20order%20right%2C%20but%20they%20also%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20because%20somebody%20that's%20buying%20a%20%2420%2C000%20ticket%20is%20not%20someone%20you%20want%20to%20upset%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20want%20that%20customer%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtto%20said%20Adaptive%20Checkout%20is%20an%20advancement%20of%20the%20company's%20existing%20fraud-detection%20products%2C%20with%20extra%20features%20designed%20to%20lower%20false%20decline%20rates%2C%20increase%20merchants'%20revenue%2C%20and%20reduce%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Otto%2C%20Riskified's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686bd5dd3d5881a51c1cc61d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224659%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Otto%20is%20Riskified's%20chief%20marketing%20officer.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Riskified%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bce8d71-a825-4796-adfa-69022b80de06%5C%22%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERiskified's%20data%20science%20team%20built%20Adaptive%20Checkout%20in-house.%20Otto%20said%20the%20company%20also%20works%20closely%20with%20its%20clients%20to%20help%20design%20tools%20to%20help%20them%20solve%20their%20most%20pressing%20problems%2C%20including%20accurate%20transaction%20approvals%20and%20fraud%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20runs%20a%20customer%20advisory%20board%20with%20some%20of%20Riskified's%20largest%20clients%2C%20which%20meets%20regularly%20to%20discuss%20trends%2C%20new%20fraud%20cases%2C%20and%20ways%20to%20improve%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22417fbc89-26d7-4100-b5c1-ade416b8d461%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdaptive%20Checkout%20uses%20AI%20to%20automatically%20identify%20each%20order's%20unique%20risk%20profile%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20customer's%20shopping%20history%2C%20actual%20location%2C%20billing%20address%2C%20and%20other%20data%20points%20from%20the%20company's%20network%20of%20global%20merchants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtto%20said%20the%20AI%20tool%20adapts%20an%20online%20merchant's%20checkout%20process%20to%20the%20transaction's%20risk%20level%20and%20then%20decides%20whether%20an%20order%20is%20legitimate%20or%20fraudulent%20and%20should%20be%20approved%20or%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdaptive%20Checkout's%20AI%20helps%20TickPick%20make%20%26quot%3Bintelligent%20decisions%26quot%3B%20for%20each%20purchase%2C%20Otto%20said.%20Cases%20of%20blatant%20fraud%20are%20automatically%20declined%2C%20while%20safe%20transactions%20are%20approved.%20For%20orders%20that%20aren't%20straightforward%2C%20such%20as%20when%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20customer's%20address%20or%20payment%20source%2C%20the%20tool%20requests%20additional%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Otto%20said%20the%20AI%20might%20ask%20the%20customer%20for%20their%20card%20verification%20value%2C%20the%20three-%20or%20four-digit%20code%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20or%20to%20set%20up%20a%20one-time%20password.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20get%20that%20back%2C%20the%20order's%20approved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20taking%20an%20extra%20step%20to%20verify%20that%20a%20customer%20is%20legitimate%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20high-value%20purchase%2C%20helps%20protect%20both%20merchants%20and%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d292c450-0966-4f3c-9556-32eb9470c5c6%5C%22%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETickPick%20tracked%20the%20transactions%20that%20were%20declined%20due%20to%20fraud%20risk%20before%20and%20after%20using%20Adaptive%20Checkout.%20Otto%20said%20it%20found%20that%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20using%20the%20tool%2C%20TickPick%20was%20able%20to%20approve%20as%20much%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.riskified.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Friskified-unveils-adaptive-checkout-ai-fraud-prevention%3F_gl%3D1*fn6ift*_gcl_au*MjA5MzY3MjAxMS4xNzUxMTIwNzM4*_ga*NDE1NzM4NjY3LjE3NTExMjA3NDU.*_ga_L8RV3KLX8W*czE3NTExMjA3NDUkbzEkZzEkdDE3NTExMjA3OTMkajEyJGwwJGg2MTgwNjY3Nzg.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%243%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20incremental%20revenue%20from%20orders%20that%20it%20would%20have%20previously%20declined%20due%20to%20fraud%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtto%20said%20about%2050%20of%20Riskified's%20existing%20clients%20are%20using%20Adaptive%20Checkout%2C%20and%20Riskified%20continues%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20its%20clients%20to%20get%20feedback%20on%20new%20AI%20features%20and%20tools.%20Otto%20said%20the%20company%20is%20working%20on%20improving%20and%20adding%20new%20features%20to%20the%20tool%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Friskified-ai-fraud-detection-tickpick-falsely-declined-transactions-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insid