ges%20every%20few%20kilometres%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20start%20speaking%20about%20these%20micro%20cuisines%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dipali%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dipali%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20entertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-466536%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDipali%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20entertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20research%20and%20documentation%2C%20and%20bringing%20eyes%20to%20Rajasthani%20food%20via%20her%20informative%20Instagram%20videos%2C%20Dipali%20also%20curates%20pop-up%20travelling%20museums%2C%20which%20are%20filled%20with%20tangible%20things%20from%20across%20Rajasthan.%20There%20are%20ingredients%20and%20foods%20that%20people%20are%20free%20to%2