3ENot%20all%20of%20those%20performance%20metrics%20are%20always%20within%20a%20Flex%20driver's%20control%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BLong%20queues%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20parking%20at%20a%20delivery%20station%20or%20a%20glitching%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20on%20a%20driver's%20smartphone%20can%20negatively%20affect%20'on-time%20arrival%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20reads%2C%20referring%20to%20another%20metric%20Amazon%20uses%20to%20evaluate%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20uses%20metrics%20like%20on-time%20arrival%20to%20determine%20a%20driver's%20%26quot%3Bstanding%26quot%3B%20grade.%20The%20grade%20can%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20affect%20a%20driver's%20pay%20and%20access%20to%20future%20shifts%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20told%20BI%20that%20standing%20doesn't%20affect%20how%20much%20work%20a%20Flex%20driver%20can%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20and%20that%20grade%20accounts%20for%20circumstances%20outside%20a%20driver's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20report's%20conclusions%20is%20that%20Flex%20drivers%20are%20misclassified%20as%20independent%20contractors.%20It%20says%20they%20should%20be%20considered%20employees%20since%20Amazon's%20control%20of%20their%20working%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20through%20metric-based%20standing%2C%20means%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20truly%20in%20business%20for%20themselves%20like%20legitimate%20independent%20contractors%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGig%20workers%20are%20generally%20classified%20as%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%C2%A0gig%20work%20continues%20to%20expand.%20Retailers%20like%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWalmart%20and%20Target%20also%20have%20their%20own%20gig%20workforces%20picking%20up%20and%20delivering%20customers'%20orders.%20Apps%20that%20bring%20gig%20work%20to%20other%20industries%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-for-nursing-apps-show-issues-across-expanding-gig-economy-