px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20trained%20in%20the%20stitching%20school%20have%20now%20found%20new%20means%20of%20income%20and%20sustaining%20their%20families.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T161427.356-1751976713-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20trained%20in%20the%20stitching%20school%20have%20now%20found%20new%20means%20of%20income%20and%20are%20sustaining%20their%20families.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20participatory%20model%2C%20she%20explained%2C%20ensures%20transparency%20and%20connection.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20donors%20know%20exactly%20where%20the%20money%20goes%20%E2%80%94%20into%20machines%2C%20materials%2C%20trainers%E2%80%99%20salaries%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20tea%20for%20the%20learners.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStitching%20futures%2C%20one%20garment%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20over%20two%20years%2C%20SAHAS%20has%20trained%20more%20than%20100%20women.%20Some%20now%20work%20independently%20from%20home%2C%2