tise%20on%20a%20range%20of%20different%20topics%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbico%20Ice%20Factory%20(as%20it%20was%20known%20then)%20enjoyed%20its%20popularity%20for%20decades%20before%20a%20factory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ice%2C%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20was%20stored%20in%20ice%20houses%20in%20Mumbai%20but%20India%E2%80%99s%20heat%20posed%20a%20challenge.%20So%2C%20businessmen%20Nanabhoy%20Byramjee%20Jeejeebhoy%20and%20JA%20Forbes%20launched%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20first%20ice%20factory%20in%20Ballard%20Estate%20in%201878.%20It%20was%20christened%20%E2%80%98Bombay%20Ice%20Manufacturing%20Co%E2%80%99%20before%20being%20rebranded%20as%20%E2%80%98Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%202019%2C%20when%20Malik%20first%20set%20sight%20on%20the%20building%2C%20he%20acquired%20it%20but%20with%20no%20plans%20to%20renovate%20or%20repurpose%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366166%2Fcossimbazar-palace-of-roys-rajbari-murshidabad-west-bengal-ancestral-palaces-heritage-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiece%20of%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20banyan%20tree%2C%20however%2C%20would%20etch%20an%20image%20in%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20mind%20that%20would%20eventually%20become%20the%20seed%20that%20would%20reinvigorate%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%2C%20whatsoever%2C%20of%20either%20acquiring%20such%20a%20space%20or%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20with%20it.%20But%20the%20image%20of%20the%20banyan%20tree%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Malik%20found%20himself%20saying%20a%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20project%2C%20joined%20by%20Abhijit%20Meh