unteers-restore-pond-wildlife-ujjain-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatured%20in%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20embedded%20in%20the%20glass%20floor%20towards%20the%20entrance.%20Another%20treasure%20lay%20in%20uncovering%20the%20historic%20gantry%20that%20once%20facilitated%20the%20transport%20of%20ice%20slabs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20room%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98giant%20ice%20tray%E2%80%99%20where%20ice%20was%20manufactured.%20There%20were%20four-foot-deep%20pits%20with%20refrigerant%20coils%20running%20alongside%20that%20would%20freeze%20the%20water%20in%20the%20pits.%20The%20massive%20ice%20blocks%20were%20then%20picked%20up%20using%20a%20crane%20and%20moved%20to%20an%20area%20where%20they%20would%20be%20cut%20and%20distributed%20for%20their%20final%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%20During%20restoration%2C%20the%20raised%20floor%20was%20wood%20panelled%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20to%20reveal%20the%20pits.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20architect%E2%80%99s%20lens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-54-1751977719.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20restoration%20process%20took%20a%20total%20of%20two%20years%20before%20IF.BE%20was%20deemed%20ready%20to%20host%20events%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-54-1751977719.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-54-1751977719-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-54-1751977719-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-54-1751977719-768x402.jp