-one-tree-uttar-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Andhra-Based%20Chocolate%20Brand%20Empowered%20300%2B%20Farmers%20%26amp%3B%20Earned%20Rs%208.7%20Cr%20in%20Year%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBehind%20every%20chocolate%20bar%20lies%20the%20story%20of%20a%20farmer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20%3Cem%3EManam%20Chocolate%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20story%20begins%20in%20the%20cocoa%20farms%20of%20West%20Godavari%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Belgian%20nor%20Swiss%2C%20this%20chocolate%20is%20proudly%20and%20entirely%20Indian.%20With%20over%20300%20products%20across%2050%20categories%2C%20Manam%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262803%2Fmumbai-woman-entrepreneur-healthy-snacks-oats-flax-seeds-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChocolate%20is%20redefining%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20perception%20of%20Indian-origin%20cocoa%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20And%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it%20is%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20craft%2C%20community%2C%20and%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2015%2C%202023%2C%20Manam%20Chocolate%20launched%20its%20first%20collection%20in%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Banjara%20Hills%20%E2%80%94%20a%20proud%20tribute%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20made%20it%20all%20possible.%20Among%20its%20most%20celebrated%20offerings%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3EManam%20Signature%20Tablet%3C%2Fem%3E%20collection%2C%20featuring%2043%20unique%20bars.%20Two%20of%20these%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EFarm%20Tablet%20No.1%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ENo.3%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20made%20from%20beans%20grown%20by%20farmers%20D%20Hari%20Krishna%20and%20GVS%20Prasad%2C%20each%20bar%20carrying%20the%20distinct%20flavour%20of%20a%20single%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Farm%20to%20Tablet%3A%20A%20Story%20of%20Trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Single%20Farmer%20Series%20recognises%20farms%20that%20have%20unique%20flavour%20profiles.%20The%20craft%20chocolate%20is%20about%20complexity%20and%20flavour.%20Everything%20we%20do%20is%20to%20derive%20complexity%20from%20the%20bean%20without%20adding%20anything.%20So%20these%20two%20or%20three%20farms%20we%20have%20identified%20as%20being%20interested%20enough%20in%20the%20single-farmer%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaitanya%20Muppala%2C%20CEO%20of%20Distinct%20Origins%20Private%20Limited%20(DOPL)%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20introduction%20of%20Manam%20Chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Manam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%E2%80%98we%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98us%E2%80%99%20in%20Telugu.%20The%20brand%20is%20designed%20to%20delight%20chocolate%20lovers%20and%20offers%20signature%20tablets%2C%20bonbons%2C%20truffles%2C%20nama%2C%20barks%2C%20fudge%2C%20palettes%2C%20rochers%2C%20clusters%2C%20macarons%2C%20gianduja%2C%20spreads%2C%20cakes%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20viennoiserie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201650px)%20100vw%2C%201650px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754.jpg%201650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465028%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20of%20cocoa%20beans%20from%20farm%20to%20fermentery%20and%20shaping%20into%20a%20chocolate%20tablet%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20feasible%20without%20farmers%E2%80%99%20invaluable%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20of%20cocoa%20beans%20from%20farm%20to%20fermentery%20and%20shaping%20into%20a%20chocolate%20tablet%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20feasible%20without%20these%20farmers%E2%80%99%20invaluable%20support.%20We%20appreciate%20their%20hard%20work.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20making%20a%20high-value%20product%20from%20their%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20chocolatier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrafting%20Chocolate%2C%20Rooted%20in%20Mithai%20shop%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20earning%20his%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20General%20Business%20Management%20from%20Sauder%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20completing%20the%20Stanford%20Seed%20Program%20from%20the%20Stanford%20University%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Business%E2%80%99s%20Institute%20for%20Innovation%20in%20Developing%20Economies%2C%20Muppala%20came%20back%20to%20India%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20was%20briefly%20unwell%2C%20so%20he%20started%20spending%20time%20in%20the%20business%20his%20father%20owned%2C%20%E2%80%93%20Almond%20House%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F265150%2Feasy-homemade-traditional-diwali-sweets-recipes-laddoo-coconut-til-oats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emithai%20(sweet)%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20small%20business%20with%20a%20single%20store.%20While%20resolving%20its%20drawbacks%2C%20he%20inadvertently%20formed%20a%20bond%20with%20it%20before%20he%20could%20realize.%20The%20business%20flourished%20under%20his%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201650px)%20100vw%2C%201650px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760.jpg%201650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChaitanya-Muppala_Founder-Manam-Chocolate-CEO-Distinct-Origins-Pvt-Ltd_photo-credit-Daksh-Chindalia-_7_11zon-1751876760-15