%20chocolate%20provides%20no%20information%20about%20the%20source%20of%20the%20cocoa%20bean%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkhana%20is%20now%20reaping%20the%20rewards.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20company%2C%20which%20employs%20around%20200%20people%2C%20recorded%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs.%208.79%20crore%2C%20achieved%20in%20only%20eight%20months%20of%20operation%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24.%20The%20chocolate%20maker%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20growing%20150%25%20year-on-year.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20successful%20market%20strategy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imports%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20its%20cocoa%20needs%20despite%20having%20grown%20cocoa%20for%20over%20six%20decades.%20Muppala%20recently%20started%20exporting%20beans%20to%20the%20world.%20This%20February%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20major%20consignment%20of%20fine%20flavoured%20cocoa%20has%20been%20exported%20from%20India%20to%20Switzerland%2C%20where%20a%20major%20Swiss%20chocolate%20brand%20is%20making%20a%20single-origin%20India%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20farmers%2C%20fermenters%2C%20chocolate%20makers%2C%20chocolatiers%2C%20and%20storytellers.%20We%20see%20ourselves%20as%20craftspeople.%20Starting%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20who%20craft%20at%20the%20source%2C%20then%20a%20fermenter%2C%20then%20a%20chocolate%20maker.%20Our%20story%20starts%20on%20the%20farms.%20Every%20store%20we%20open%2C%20our%20farmer%20has%20to%20open%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20the%20chocolate%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20create%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20agro-climatic%20conditions%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoyapati%20Venkateswara%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20member%20farmers%20associated%20with%20Distinct%20Origins%2C%20who%20owns%20one%20of%20the%20first%20organic%20cocoa%20farm%20in%20West%20Godavari%20District%20in%20AP%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20we%20relied%20heavily%20on%20chemical%20sprays%20and%20fertilizers%20to%20keep%20the%20cacao%20plants%20healthy.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20started%20returning%20to%20more%20natural%2C%20sustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20further%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20found%20that%20using%20vermicompost%20significantly%20improves%20soil%20health%2C%20strengthens%20the%20trees%2C%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20active.%20We%20also%20apply%20coconut%20husk%20mulch%20around%20the%20base%20of%20each%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20it%20helps%20retain%20soil%20moisture%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20cool%20during%20hot%20weather.%20The%20result%20is%20better%20fruit%20size%2C%20more%20consistent%20pod%20quality%2C%20and%20overall%20healthier%20trees.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-500x342.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-500x342.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-300x205.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_1